cs.OS, cs.DC, cs.PF, cs.NI, cs.SY

The paper discusses the challenges of achieving low-latency computing, which is a key concern in operating systems (cs.OS) and distributed computing (cs.DC). It also touches on performance metrics (cs.PF) and hardware (cs.NI) considerations. Finally, the paper discusses the impact of system scale (cs.SY) on latency, which is a key concern in distributed systems.
